Hello Pat,

The perimeter is, as you calculated, 2*pi units.  The area is pi square units.

One cannot  directly compare these two numbers because they have units associated with 
them.

If you  have a square of side 1 meter, its perimeter is 4 meters but its area is 1 square 
meter.


